videos.description: Amadi Udenyi falls down and hits the hook shot layup while getting fouled.
videos.headline: Pepperdine's Udenyi nails falling-down layup and the foul

videos.description: Kameron Edwards flies in from behind to block Calvin Hermanson's layup attempt and then Amadi Udenyi finishes with a bucket at the other end.
videos.headline: Pepperdine's Edwards calls the swat team on Hermanson

videos.description: Jock Landale fends off Pepperdine defenders and is able to find room to go up for the layup while collecting the foul.
videos.headline: Saint Mary's' Landale evades defenders for difficult and-1
